text: A post shared on Facebook claims the omicron variant of the coronavirus is named after military codes.
The omicron variant’s name is evidence the coronavirus pandemic is a hoax.
An image shared on Facebook allegedly shows a statement issued by the Philippines’ Department of Health (DOH) regarding the spread of the omicron variant of the coronavirus.
